CBRE is pleased to present 4/1447-1451 Sydney Road, Campbellfield, for sale. 

This is an outstanding opportunity to purchase a property located in one of the most prominent and sought-after positions within the inner north.

This office/warehouse facility is located on Sydney Road and nestled amongst retailers such as Coles, Kmart, Officeworks & Chemist Warehouse. The site has recently undergone an extensive renovation including timber flooring throughout, multiple partitioned offices and air-conditioning installed.

Property features include:
+ Total building area: 1,014sqm*
+ Warehouse space: 520sqm*
+ Multiple office/training rooms
+ 9B compliance permitting education and medical use
+ 26 on-site car spaces
+ Full staff amenity including female and male bathrooms, change room and lunch room
+ Bi-fold door facade
+ Rear container height roller doors
+ Suspended ceiling and lighting throughout

Please contact the exclusive marketing agent, CBRE, for inspections and further information.
